(105, 'Week 25: 17 – 23 February 2020','Personal Evangelism and Imperatives for Mission ','Mark 16:15, Acts 1:8 ','Mark 16:15  And he said unto them, Go ye into all the world, and preach the gospel to every creature. \n
Act 1:8  But ye shall receive power, after that the Holy Ghost is come upon you: and ye shall be witnesses unto me both in Jerusalem, and in all Judaea, and in Samaria, and unto the uttermost part of the earth.',1, 2020, '2020-2-17', '2019-10-18 16:44:00');

(106, 'Week 26: 24 February – 1 March 2020','Living in the Supernatural, Daily Walk of Miracles',' 1 Cor 2:9, Dan 11:32, Mark 16:17-18','1 Cor 2:9  But as it is written, Eye hath not seen, nor ear heard, neither have entered into the heart of man, the things which God hath prepared for them that love him.\n 
