(111, 'Week 31: 30 March -  5 April 2020','A Life of Moderation and Stewardship of Your Body','Philippians 4:4-8','“4 Rejoice in the Lord always: and again I say, Rejoice.
5 Let your moderation be known unto all men. The Lord is at hand.
